long_description: Wish camping dinners didn't involve eating off of your lap? The Eureka Owego table makes it easy to enjoy a table-side dinner without from the comfort of your campsite or tailgate location. Foldable, powder-coated steel frame and lightweight, synthetic tabletop surface provide durablility and easy setup. Tabletop features 4 built-in cup holders to keep drinks secure. Each end of the table has a zippered pocket, stash pouch and mesh beverage holder to keep condiments and drink bottles in place and within easy reach. Eureka Owego Table includes a carry bag for easy transport. Closeout.
